    {
      "text": "UFO Kamen Yakisoban: Kettler no Kuroi Inbō (UFO仮面ヤキソバン ケトラーの黒い陰謀, \"UFO Mask Yakisoban: Kettler's Dark Conspiracy\") is a 1994 beat 'em up developed by KID and published by Den’Z for the Super Famicom.",
